Preheat oven to 325 degrees F (165 degrees C). Place drummettes in a 9x13 inch baking dish. In a medium bowl, combine the soup, cilantro, onion powder, pepper and garlic salt. Mix well, and pour mixture over chicken. Bake at 325 degrees F (165 degrees C) for 1 hour, or until chicken is cooked through and juices run clear.